WEBVTT

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:18.487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

00:00:18.562 --> 00:00:22.162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.437
♪Your "same here" carries
a touch of resolve♪

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:29.412
♪Pack my bags, we can set off right now♪

00:00:29.637 --> 00:00:33.112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:36.712
♪The journey itself is what
truly matters before the destination♪

00:00:36.787 --> 00:00:40.975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

00:00:41.025 --> 00:00:42.612
♪Connect♪

00:00:42.625 --> 00:00:43.275
♪Let's go!♪

00:00:43.612 --> 00:00:47.137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

00:00:47.237 --> 00:00:50.675
♪Today, no dwelling
on negative emotions♪

00:00:50.750 --> 00:00:53.450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

00:00:55.262 --> 00:00:58.199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

00:00:59.075 --> 00:01:02.375
=Love in A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

00:01:02.675 --> 00:01:06.287
=Episode 16=

00:01:14.220 --> 00:01:16.920
Mr. Lu, we heard the Lu Group
is involved in the Ye Liang fraud case.

00:01:16.920 --> 00:01:18.040
Is that true or false?

00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:19.800
Of course it's fake news.

00:01:19.800 --> 00:01:21.280
Then, what about Ye Man's real identity?

00:01:21.280 --> 00:01:22.440
Do you know the truth, Mr. Lu?

00:01:22.440 --> 00:01:24.040
What do you mean by that?

00:01:24.040 --> 00:01:25.760
Ye Man is my wife's son.

00:01:25.760 --> 00:01:26.920
Didn't you all know that?

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:30.160
Mr. Lu, did you do a background check
on your wife when you remarried?

00:01:30.160 --> 00:01:31.240
With a net worth like yours,

00:01:31.240 --> 00:01:32.790
aren't you afraid
of bringing disaster upon yourself?

00:01:32.800 --> 00:01:33.640
That's right, Mr. Lu.

00:01:33.640 --> 00:01:34.720
Please, tell us.

00:01:34.720 --> 00:01:36.240
I'm sorry, I have another meeting.

00:01:36.480 --> 00:01:37.880
Mr. Lu!

00:01:37.880 --> 00:01:38.920
- Mr. Lu!
- Mr. Lu!

00:01:38.920 --> 00:01:40.200
Please answer us!

00:01:40.920 --> 00:01:42.320
- Mr. Ye.
- Mr. Ye.

00:01:42.320 --> 00:01:43.320
Please say a few words!

00:01:44.440 --> 00:01:46.840
My father's affairs
have nothing to do with the Lu Group.

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:49.000
And everything has already been settled.

00:01:49.520 --> 00:01:50.800
Who I am doesn't matter.

00:01:51.440 --> 00:01:52.680
Please, watch your words.

00:01:56.040 --> 00:01:58.320
Mr. Ye.

00:02:01.680 --> 00:02:02.480
Man,

00:02:03.840 --> 00:02:05.600
I've always had
a good impression of you.

00:02:05.600 --> 00:02:07.360
I hope you don't let me down.

00:02:09.760 --> 00:02:11.040
I'm sorry, Mr. Lu.

00:02:11.920 --> 00:02:12.720
All of this...

00:02:14.320 --> 00:02:15.390
I will handle it properly.

00:02:15.640 --> 00:02:16.440
Good.

00:02:16.840 --> 00:02:18.120
But you must remember,

00:02:19.080 --> 00:02:21.120
this isn't just your family matter.

00:02:21.762 --> 00:02:22.562
It is also

00:02:23.880 --> 00:02:24.920
our family matter.

00:02:26.680 --> 00:02:27.480
Understood.

00:02:43.960 --> 00:02:44.680
Ms. Liu,

00:02:45.120 --> 00:02:47.240
are you getting rid
of all these clothes?

00:02:47.640 --> 00:02:48.600
Yes, Miss.

00:02:48.760 --> 00:02:51.400
Mrs. Lu told me to throw out
the clothes she doesn't want.

00:02:52.400 --> 00:02:54.240
Money doesn't grow on trees.

00:02:54.920 --> 00:02:55.680
Leave them there.

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:57.620
I'll pick some out later
to donate to the mountains.

00:02:57.640 --> 00:02:58.480
Of course, Miss.

00:03:20.300 --> 00:03:21.720
Wait for me for another ten minutes.

00:03:21.720 --> 00:03:22.680
I'll be there soon.

00:04:16.840 --> 00:04:17.360
Hello?

00:04:17.360 --> 00:04:18.520
This is Dr. Zhang's assistant.

00:04:18.520 --> 00:04:19.720
How can I help you?

00:04:20.040 --> 00:04:21.960
Hello, I'm Huang Qingbai's daughter.

00:04:21.960 --> 00:04:24.680
My mother left
some personal items at the hospital.

00:04:24.800 --> 00:04:26.120
But I can't find your location.

00:04:26.120 --> 00:04:27.880
What is your specific address?

00:04:27.880 --> 00:04:29.280
We are at 23 Huixing Road.

00:04:29.280 --> 00:04:30.160
There is a T-junction.

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:31.480
Turn right and go straight,
and you'll see the hospital.

00:04:31.480 --> 00:04:32.480
Do you need me to come pick you up?

00:04:32.480 --> 00:04:33.080
No need.

00:04:33.080 --> 00:04:34.560
I'll be there soon. Thank you.

00:04:38.200 --> 00:04:39.400
Hey, Ms. Lu, you're here.

00:04:39.640 --> 00:04:40.760
You're Tian, right?

00:04:40.760 --> 00:04:41.560
Yes.

00:04:41.880 --> 00:04:42.880
Keep up the good work.

00:04:48.120 --> 00:04:49.360
He's in a bad mood today.

00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:50.360
Don't go and disturb him.

00:04:51.590 --> 00:04:53.080
Your outfit looks quite nice on you.

00:05:05.480 --> 00:05:06.400
Ye Man,

00:05:06.840 --> 00:05:08.040
I have something to tell you.

00:05:09.520 --> 00:05:10.320
What is it?

00:05:11.720 --> 00:05:13.080
(Hai City Medical Institution Clinical Report)
Your mother isn't pregnant.

00:05:13.800 --> 00:05:15.880
We can finally be together openly.

00:05:20.480 --> 00:05:22.120
Once this is exposed,

00:05:22.480 --> 00:05:24.240
nothing can stand in our way.

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:32.880
Zhu, do you think

00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:35.360
we can stay together forever?

00:05:41.120 --> 00:05:42.640
What do you mean?

00:05:44.320 --> 00:05:45.200
I mean...

00:05:47.680 --> 00:05:49.680
We ignored our parents' relationship

00:05:49.960 --> 00:05:51.800
and public opinion,

00:05:53.840 --> 00:05:55.200
being together so recklessly.

00:05:56.800 --> 00:05:58.160
What if we break up one day?

00:06:03.800 --> 00:06:05.400
We won't.

00:06:07.640 --> 00:06:08.560
What if we do?

00:06:13.760 --> 00:06:15.400
Was everything between us before

00:06:17.840 --> 00:06:19.600
all just a lie?

00:06:24.520 --> 00:06:25.960
So,

00:06:27.320 --> 00:06:29.312
are you breaking up with me now?

00:06:30.762 --> 00:06:36.912
♪Time after time,
I repeat the same mistakes♪

00:06:37.725 --> 00:06:42.400
♪It's because I'm too persistent♪

00:06:42.950 --> 00:06:48.175
♪That I'm falling♪

00:06:49.940 --> 00:06:53.940
♪This whirlpool of love♪

00:06:54.750 --> 00:06:59.312
♪I want to escape, but I can't♪

00:06:59.440 --> 00:07:00.400
Have we

00:07:02.400 --> 00:07:03.640
ever really been together?

00:07:14.550 --> 00:07:18.862
♪It's because I'm too persistent♪

00:07:19.050 --> 00:07:24.750
♪That I'm falling♪

00:07:26.375 --> 00:07:30.825
♪This whirlpool of love♪

00:07:31.050 --> 00:07:40.200
♪I want to escape, but I can't♪

00:07:59.040 --> 00:08:00.240
I just saw your sister

00:08:00.240 --> 00:08:01.320
run out crying.

00:08:02.220 --> 00:08:03.560
Have you really made up your mind?

00:08:12.960 --> 00:08:14.920
Well, everyone is telling me

00:08:16.080 --> 00:08:18.080
what's best for her.

00:08:18.880 --> 00:08:20.680
If I don't listen, is that too selfish?

00:08:23.240 --> 00:08:24.720
Since you've made your decision,

00:08:25.880 --> 00:08:27.480
pull yourself together.

00:08:27.500 --> 00:08:29.040
The roadshow is less than a week away.

00:08:31.000 --> 00:08:32.400
The matter regarding your father

00:08:32.400 --> 00:08:34.040
has already reached Mr. Lu's ears.

00:08:35.480 --> 00:08:37.800
What you're looking for
will only get harder to find.

00:08:42.360 --> 00:08:44.520
We discussed the industrial concept
of smart logistics

00:08:44.520 --> 00:08:47.200
and the smart logistics industry
development environment and analysis.

00:08:47.200 --> 00:08:47.920
Also...

00:08:47.920 --> 00:08:48.720
Alright.

00:08:48.960 --> 00:08:49.760
How about this?

00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:51.240
If anything comes up next time,

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:53.160
just report to Vice President Zhang.

00:08:53.960 --> 00:08:55.125
Understood, Mr. Lu.

00:08:57.080 --> 00:08:59.280
Mr. Lu, it's time
for the meeting with Mr. Hu from BOC.

00:08:59.280 --> 00:09:00.360
Alright, I've got it.

00:09:02.520 --> 00:09:03.320
How about this?

00:09:03.720 --> 00:09:05.440
Whatever happens
on your end from now on,

00:09:05.440 --> 00:09:06.480
don't report it to me.

00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:07.560
Make the decisions yourself.

00:09:08.600 --> 00:09:09.520
Okay.

00:10:30.960 --> 00:10:32.880
Mr. Lu, did the meeting end that quickly?

00:10:33.080 --> 00:10:34.880
My high blood pressure
flared up. I'm dizzy.

00:10:35.440 --> 00:10:36.440
Cancel the meeting.

00:10:53.300 --> 00:10:57.800
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

00:10:58.025 --> 00:11:01.813
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

00:11:01.988 --> 00:11:06.063
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

00:11:06.063 --> 00:11:10.200
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

00:11:10.325 --> 00:11:14.100
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

00:11:14.100 --> 00:11:17.875
♪I'll learn to stop longing
for what's gone♪

00:11:17.875 --> 00:11:20.150
♪The you in my memories♪

00:11:20.150 --> 00:11:22.163
♪Will fade from clarity♪

00:11:22.163 --> 00:11:27.600
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

00:11:29.163 --> 00:11:34.600
♪Forget you completely♪